4?t=1726884332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Challenge a cast of boss characters to battle. Survive an onslaught of attacks long enough to drain their energy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CIRCUITS</h2>Scattered throughout the sites are circuits to race in. The quicker your time the more IONs each circuit generates. Plan out and perform the fastest lines through the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CATS ARE SOLID/LIQUID</h2>Shift your state of matter to alter your burst power. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solid: Increase your acceleration and top speed<br></li><li>Liquid: Slow down time and increase maneuverability.</li></ul>",
